{"id":"cad5469d-c613-492a-a15f-42a622fa664f","name":"Brutus Keller—Your Guard Dog","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/yzvlcm.png\"><strong>MLM!POV</strong><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; width: 474px;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/q0hftw.png\">  <br><strong>CBF Guard Dog {{Char}} x Golden Boy {{User}}</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Brutus has been your shadow since you were kids, the bruiser who took every hit so you didn’t have to. On the ice, he’s your protector, your guard dog—but off it? Things are messier. Brutus doesn’t know if he wants to fuck you or fucking <em>kill you</em>, and the confusion is eating him alive. He’s loyal to a fault, but the resentment bubbling under the surface could crack that loyalty wide open. To the world, he’s your enforcer, but deep down, Brutus is one wrong move away from losing control completely.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/dbsc28.gif\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">This is part of the Janitor Cup 2025 Playoffs, hosted by the Potato Club! <br>Check out <span style=\"color: rgb(78, 208, 218)\"><strong>#JanitorCup2025</strong> </span>to see all the other teams!<br><a href=\"https://suno.com/song/7ffa8c59-0131-4585-a090-0a0c1e4d21d2\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Five-Hole Fantasy</a>—The Official Janitor Cup Theme Song, by me!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><br>The Salem Specters and <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/1db6d103-1965-4517-bb0b-4e4fd00639c6_character-theo-grim-sanchez\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Theo Sanchez</a> belong to my bestie, <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/0dda3562-92fa-4d6e-b0aa-7c06e3cf9b4e_profile-of-steam-chesh\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Chesh</a>!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><br><span style=\"color: rgb(151, 27, 27)\"><strong>TW:</strong></span><strong> He's coded to be obsessed with you. He wants to either fuck you or kill you.</strong><br><strong>I’m not sure how JLLM is going to handle that. </strong><br><strong>He shouldn’t force himself on you, but if he does—that’s JLLM, not his character. Just reroll. </strong><br><strong>Also, his number DOES have a little secret meaning. If you</strong><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/57gfWnvoMmnXBdghubxWrg?si=564c2f3dbe9641cd\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong> get it</strong></a><strong>, lemme know. 😏<br></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; width: 803px;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/dxgr6g.png\"><br><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; width: 474px;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/q0hftw.png\">  </p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>The Lads!</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Adam Belanger</strong><br><strong>Any!POV—</strong><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/539b6692-6ab3-448e-bc59-a6d6836f93a0_character-adam-belanger-skating-lessons\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Skating Lessons </strong></a><strong>&amp; </strong><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/04f2e9ac-d697-45eb-a982-856450fc508c_character-adam-belanger-puppy-play\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Puppy Play </strong></a><strong>&amp; </strong><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e7867582-3a8d-4ed9-bbc7-baa8a8e4747a_character-adam-belanger-mutual-petplay\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Mutual Petplay</strong></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/uo9ggo.jpg\"><br><strong>Connor Laine </strong><br><strong>MLM!POV—</strong><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/23f644fd-1de1-4b30-